nd}} reprise their roles as [[Other (Chitauri) (Earth-199999)|The Other]] and [[Carina (Earth-199999)|Carina]], the Collector's aide, respectively.<ref name="Lovibond Confirmed"/> {{WP|Josh Brolin}} makes an uncredited appearance as [[Thanos (Earth-199999)|Thanos]]<ref>{{cite|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/josh-brolin-to-play-thanos-in-marvels-guardians-of-the-galaxy-1201198891/|title=Josh Brolin to Play Thanos in Marvel's 'Guardians of the Galaxy'|date=30 May 2014|accessdate=30 May 2014|last=Kroll|first=Justin|work=Variety}}</ref> Fred the Dog appears as [[Cosmo (Earth-199999)|Cosmo]]. {{WP|Rob Zombie}}, {{WP|Raed Abbas}}, and {{WP|Bruce Mackinnon}} appear as [[Ravagers (Earth-199999)|Ravagers]]. Director [[James Gunn]] portrays a [[Sakaarans|Sakaaran]] soldier and Dancing Baby Groot. In the post-credits scene, {{WP|Seth Green}} voices [[Howard Duckson (Earth-199999)|Howard the Duck]] in an uncredited role.

